		{"id":"a2","type":"text","text":"**A2 — Entity Extraction** (daily 6:30 AM)\nNews → Sonnet 4.6 → entities\n→ `topic_clusters` + `keywords`","x":0,"y":10,"width":360,"height":80,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"h","type":"text","text":"**H — GSC Export**\nSearch Console → 7-day CSV\n→ `gsc-exports/latest.csv`","x":400,"y":10,"width":280,"height":80,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"cluster-json","type":"text","text":"**flagship-clusters/{slug}.json**\nCandidates → promote → targets","x":180,"y":620,"width":320,"height":70,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"path1","type":"text","text":"## Path 1: Reactive (D)\n`generate-seo.ts` · **daily 9 AM**\n\n**Fully automatic** gap-fill\nfrom keyword inventory\n\nTop 10 clusters (mention ≥ 2)\nMax 8 pages/run · EN + ZH\n\n**Generates:**\n- Glossary (pillar topic)\n- FAQ (brave-discussion / blog)\n- Compare (vs pattern / blog)\n- Topic Hub (mention ≥ 5)","x":0,"y":820,"width":340,"height":280,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"path2","type":"text","text":"## Path 2: Proactive (F)\n`generate-seo.ts --cluster`\n**Manual / on-demand**\n\n**Source-grounded** generation\nResolution: curated → Exa\n→ Brave → empty\n\n**Generates:**\n- Cornerstone (2000–4000 tok)\n- Glossary\n- FAQ\n- Compare\nMax 8 pages/run","x":380,"y":820,"width":300,"height":280,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"comparison","type":"text","text":"### Path 1 vs Path 2\n\n| | Path 1 (Daily) | Path 2 (Cluster) |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Curation** | Fully automatic | Human-curated |\n| **Source material** | LLM knowledge only | Fetched + grounded |\n| **Scope** | Any cluster ≥ 2 mentions | Flagship topics |\n| **Quality** | Commodity SEO | Higher quality |","x":0,"y":1240,"width":680,"height":160},
		{"id":"g-exec","type":"text","text":"**G — Execution**\nRe-generate with fresh sources\nEN + ZH independently\nPreserves internal links","x":380,"y":1530,"width":300,"height":120,"color":"2"},
