		{"id":"e","type":"text","text":"## E — Cluster Discovery\n`planner.ts` · 6-stage pipeline\n\n| Stage | Source |\n|---|---|\n| 1 | SERP demand (Serper.dev) |\n| 2 | Exa semantic gap |\n| 3 | Competitor audit (LLM) |\n| 4 | News signals (14-day) |\n| 5 | GSC unmatched queries |\n| 6 | Score 0–100 + promote/dismiss |","x":0,"y":290,"width":440,"height":220,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"j","type":"text","text":"**J — Weekly Strategy**\nGap analysis +\nBrave demand\nvalidation\n→ content plan","x":480,"y":290,"width":200,"height":140,"color":"3"},
